            <thetext>The &quot;cellContextmenu&quot; event which reacts on the &quot;contextMenu&quot; event is not fired. The &quot;__lastMouseDownCell&quot; map on which the executing of this event relies is emptied before.

In the current event sequence the following handler are called

1)  _onMouseDownPane
2) _onMouseupFocusIndicator
3) _onContextMenu

within the second handler the &quot;__lastMouseDownCell&quot; map is emptied.</thetext>
